---
import HeaderBackgroundImage from "../../components/shared/header-background-image.astro";
import SectionTitle from "../../components/shared/section-title.astro";
import DemoForm from "./DemoForm.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative max-w-480 z-30 mx-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden min-h-200"
>
  <HeaderBackgroundImage
    class="absolute bottom-96 left-0 w-full h-full object-contain"
  />

  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-100 lg:w-150 flex">
    <div class="w-full z-10 h-full border border-dashed border-dashed-border">
    </div>

    <div class="w-full z-10 h-full border border-dashed border-dashed-border">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-480 h-full relative pt-15 mx-auto flex flex-col items-center gap-8 overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="z-30 flex flex-col mb-10 items-center text-center">
      <SectionTitle class="max-sm:text-[32px] max-sm:leading-10"
        >Get Demo</SectionTitle
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto w-80 md:w-150 text-center">
    <div
      class="font-outfit text-xl text-center text-title-section mb-2 fade-in-scroll"
    >
      We'd love to hear from you
    </div>
    <div class="text-lg font-outfit text-subtitle fade-in-scroll">
      This isn’t a generic product tour. We tailor the session to your
      compliance experience and goals, whether you’re preparing for your first
      audit or scaling a multi-framework program across teams.
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center my-6 fade-in-scroll">
      <div class="font-outfit text-base font-semibold text-title-section mb-3">
        What We’ll Cover in Your Session:
      </div>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-subtitle">
          <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"
          ></span>
          Structuring and mapping multiple compliance frameworks in one program
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-subtitle">
          <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"
          ></span>
          Evidence collection and task workflows aligned to real teams
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-subtitle">
          <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"
          ></span>
          Vendor, asset, and personnel tracking with Registry
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-subtitle">
          <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"
          ></span>
          Trust Center with NDA-based document sharing
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-subtitle">
          <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"
          ></span>
          How Openlane fits into your existing processes and infrastructure
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-subtitle">
          <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"
          ></span>
          Dedicated time for your specific goals, questions, and requirements
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto z-30"><DemoForm /></div>
</section>
